info.name: Chinese Checkers
info.attribution: The game layout, game board, and library image were done by LawDawg and released to the Public Domain under CC0. The background, solid marble, and shiny 1 marble are from the VirtualTabletop assets and are in the Public Domain by CC0. The shiny 2 and shiny 3 marbles are by mousewax and are in the Public Domain by CC0.
info.description: Jump over own or opponent pieces to move to opposite side of board.  First to relocate all 10 pieces wins.
info.helpText: Players take seat. Press gear icon to choose marble style. Move one desired colored marble to end point of board. Press START. After player ends turn, click Next Player button to advance turn.

fields.text: Choose marble style. Restart new game after changing styles.
